msgid ""
"A free port is selected randomly on first installation. The saved value "
"remains unchanged after restarts."
msgstr "首次安装时会随机选择一个空闲端口。保存后重启不会改变该端口。"

#: luci-app-axonhub/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/axonhub.js:303
msgid ""
"A soft runtime limit that leaves memory available for routing and other "
"services."
msgstr "为 Go 运行时设置软限制，给路由和其他服务保留内存。"

