#: luci-app-axonhub/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/axonhub.js:286
msgid ""
"Changing this path starts a separate instance unless the existing database "
"is moved while AxonHub is stopped."
msgstr ""
"修改此路径会创建一个全新实例；如需保留数据，请先停止 AxonHub，再移动现有数据"
"库。"

